lines.text:
[Watching Randall's daughter enter a car]
Smart money says the real action's in the car with the boyfriend.

[Deadpan]
I think the smart money should shut up.

[holds up a yo-yo]
what do you think this is?
It's just a simple toy man
To you it is. But back in 1500 in the Philippines it was a weapon
[lashes out with the yo-yo and smashes the bottle Dontae is drinking from]
